

---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Contact HSL Innovations for app support, bug reports, feedback, and general questions."
>
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h1>Get in touch.</h1>
    <p>
      Have a question, bug report, feature request, or feedback about an
      HSL Innovations app? Use the contact options below.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <h2>App Support</h2>
    <p>
      For help with Flora Endless Word Search or any HSL Innovations app, please
      include the app name, your device model, iOS or iPadOS version, and a short
      description of the issue.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="mailto:hslinnovations@icloud.com">hslinnovations@icloud.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Bug Reports</h2>
    <p>
      When reporting a bug, please include the steps that led to the issue, what
      you expected to happen, and what actually happened. Screenshots are helpful
      when available.
    </p>

    <h2>Feedback and Feature Requests</h2>
    <p>
      HSL Innovations apps are improved through real feedback. Suggestions for
      new features, accessibility improvements, usability changes, and future app
      ideas are welcome.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy Questions</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy-related questions, please review the <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policies</a> page or contact HSL Innovations at
      the support email above.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>